&lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( tamil : mother 's order ) is a tamil language drama film starring sivaji ganesan , savitri and pandari bai in the lead roles . the film , directed by ch . narayana murthy , had musical score by s. m. subbaiah naidu and was released on 4 july 1958 . the film won national film award for best feature film in tamil in 1959 .